description: Get process information by its ID for a specific scaled-out instance in a web site.

instance_id.description: ID of a specific scaled-out instance. This is the value of the name property in the JSON response from 'GET api/sites/{siteName}/instances'.

resource_group_name.description: Name of the resource group to which the resource belongs.

subscription_id.description: Your Azure subscription ID. This is a GUID-formatted string (e.g. 00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000).
